{"body":[{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕组 搬运」\n（禁止在B站宣传漫游相关内容，否则拉黑）","location":2,"from":0,"to":5},{"content":"无论任何风景映照在眼底","from":5.63,"location":2,"to":10.552},{"content":"都像是繁星最后闪现的光辉","from":10.552,"location":2,"to":15.64},{"content":"事到如今达观都添了几分庸俗","from":15.64,"location":2,"to":20.812},{"content":"在黑暗的夜里 任谁都得怀着明灯才行","from":20.812,"location":2,"to":26.609},{"content":"无人知晓 也没有名字的","from":27.068,"location":2,"to":31.823},{"content":"我们的火花 稍微照亮的","from":32.24,"location":2,"to":36.953},{"content":"是干枯的大地 焦黑的瓦砾","from":36.953,"location":2,"to":42.459},{"content":"以及确实曾有欢笑的你的每一天","from":42.459,"location":2,"to":46.463},{"content":"在境界线的另一侧","from":46.463,"location":2,"to":49.883},{"content":"被遗忘的终焉","from":49.883,"location":2,"to":55.096},{"content":"全都已经知道","from":55.096,"location":2,"to":57.432},{"content":"就连屈服也不被允许的那道声音","from":57.432,"location":2,"to":62.562},{"content":"是来自过去的战友 还是自己的心","from":62.562,"location":2,"to":67.15},{"content":"存在意义终究不是建立在自己身上","from":67.15,"location":2,"to":72.781},{"content":"就像是你 只有那道声音","from":73.156,"location":2,"to":77.994},{"content":"既然在足以触碰的距离","from":77.994,"location":2,"to":80.497},{"content":"就算只是微弱亮起的火光","from":80.497,"location":2,"to":83.166},{"content":"我觉得都能称作希望","from":83.166,"location":2,"to":88.088},{"content":"很好, 就是这样","from":98.098,"location":2,"to":99.432},{"content":"(特别军官学校 战技演练场)","from":99.432,"location":2,"to":99.808},{"content":"接下来要再更深入\n(特别军官学校 战技演练场)","from":99.808,"location":2,"to":101.35},{"content":"就这样紧追上去\n(特别军官学校 战技演练场)","from":101.35,"location":2,"to":102.85},{"content":"收到","from":103.144,"location":2,"to":104.104},{"content":"要绕过去吗","from":108.274,"location":2,"to":109.317},{"content":"臭铁罐们, 等著瞧吧","from":110.86,"location":2,"to":113.071},{"content":"我马上就往你那屁股开一个大洞啦","from":113.071,"location":2,"to":116.574},{"content":"等等, 马塞尔","from":122.58,"location":2,"to":123.915},{"content":"就快撞上了","from":123.915,"location":2,"to":125.375},{"content":"得救了…","from":145.145,"location":2,"to":146.813},{"content":"痛死啦…","from":147.313,"location":2,"to":149.232},{"content":"抱歉, 尤金","from":149.566,"location":2,"to":150.65},{"content":"你没事吧","from":150.984,"location":2,"to":151.943},{"content":"还好啦…","from":152.318,"location":2,"to":153.611},{"content":"你们到底在做什么","from":153.611,"location":2,"to":156.739},{"content":"立刻给我从机体下来","from":156.739,"location":2,"to":159.075},{"content":"马塞尔候补生","from":164.87,"location":2,"to":166.382},{"content":"你刚才是想做什么\n(星历2149年 2月11日)","from":166.416,"location":2,"to":168.2},{"content":"我想绕到敌军的背后…","from":168.209,"location":2,"to":170.461},{"content":"所以就越过山丘了吗","from":171.087,"location":2,"to":172.881},{"content":"还将机甲的肚子袒露在敌军面前","from":173.214,"location":2,"to":175.925},{"content":"你这次的模拟战是零分","from":176.885,"location":2,"to":179.429},{"content":"给我去重新从基础学起","from":179.429,"location":2,"to":181.347},{"content":"是","from":181.681,"location":2,"to":182.39},{"content":"接着是诺赞候补生","from":182.39,"location":2,"to":184.309},{"content":"你竟然让破坏之杖 做出那种跳跃机动动作","from":184.314,"location":2,"to":186.56},{"content":"到底在想什么啊","from":186.561,"location":2,"to":187.812},{"content":"是要把机体搞坏吗","from":187.812,"location":2,"to":189.189},{"content":"我认为要避免对撞就只能那么做了","from":189.564,"location":2,"to":192.692},{"content":"与其失去两架机体","from":194.027,"location":2,"to":195.904},{"content":"让其中一架的脚部毁损带来的伤害","from":195.904,"location":2,"to":198.406},{"content":"还比较低吧","from":198.406,"location":2,"to":199.616},{"content":"辛…","from":199.616,"location":2,"to":200.45},{"content":"是没错","from":200.742,"location":2,"to":202.035},{"content":"设法回避对撞这点是值得赞许","from":203.203,"location":2,"to":205.955},{"content":"但你进行了危险操纵也是事实","from":206.372,"location":2,"to":209.5},{"content":"因此你也是零分","from":209.5,"location":2,"to":211.085},{"content":"知道吗","from":211.294,"location":2,"to":212.045},{"content":"是","from":212.337,"location":2,"to":213.004},{"content":"诺赞","from":217.592,"location":2,"to":218.509},{"content":"我可不会向你道谢","from":221.387,"location":2,"to":223.223},{"content":"没那必要","from":223.723,"location":2,"to":224.891},{"content":"而且就算你没有避开, 我也可以…","from":224.891,"location":2,"to":227.018},{"content":"所以我就说没那必要","from":227.018,"location":2,"to":229.062},{"content":"走吧, 尤金","from":231.856,"location":2,"to":233.316},{"content":"好啦, 走了啦","from":234.108,"location":2,"to":235.485},{"content":"好青春啊, 真是不错","from":238.196,"location":2,"to":240.323},{"content":"看上去是那样吗","from":240.865,"location":2,"to":242.533},{"content":"你还真是不坦率耶","from":243.326,"location":2,"to":244.702},{"content":"今天有什么事?","from":246.537,"location":2,"to":247.538},{"content":"希望你能再跟我来一趟","from":247.538,"location":2,"to":249.374},{"content":"我有得到许可","from":249.374,"location":2,"to":250.75},{"content":"尤金, 你还是跟诺赞保持距离比较好","from":253.795,"location":2,"to":256.631},{"content":"为什么","from":256.631,"location":2,"to":257.674},{"content":"你应该也知道吧","from":257.674,"location":2,"to":259.384},{"content":"86那些家伙参与开发的新型机甲…","from":259.801,"location":2,"to":263.596},{"content":"那真的很不得了","from":263.888,"location":2,"to":265.223},{"content":"是以共和国的机体为原型做成的","from":265.223,"location":2,"to":267.225},{"content":"根本没在顾虑驾驶员的疯狂兵器","from":267.225,"location":2,"to":270.311},{"content":"听说被派去试驾的已经死了一票人了","from":270.728,"location":2,"to":275.358},{"content":"但就只有那些家伙还活得好好的","from":275.858,"location":2,"to":278.778},{"content":"那不过是谣传啦","from":278.778,"location":2,"to":280.196},{"content":"即使如此","from":280.738,"location":2,"to":282.031},{"content":"那家伙还是给我很讨厌的感觉","from":283.366,"location":2,"to":285.368},{"content":"简直就像…","from":286.577,"location":2,"to":287.578},{"content":"像什么","from":288.204,"location":2,"to":289.163},{"content":"就像死神一样","from":293.001,"location":2,"to":294.335},{"content":"你们几个","from":299.799,"location":2,"to":300.925},{"content":"可以来一下吗","from":302.844,"location":2,"to":304.178},{"content":"(星历2149年 4月1日)","from":305.096,"location":2,"to":308.099},{"content":"这是要开去哪里啊","from":309.767,"location":2,"to":311.978},{"content":"要打模拟战吗","from":311.978,"location":2,"to":312.937},{"content":"天晓得","from":312.937,"location":2,"to":313.855},{"content":"但那边好像拉着什么耶","from":314.022,"location":2,"to":316.441},{"content":"你是说有布盖着的那个吗","from":317.15,"location":2,"to":318.818},{"content":"你们途经的时候","from":323.531,"location":2,"to":325.366},{"content":"这里还是军团的支配区域","from":325.366,"location":2,"to":327.285},{"content":"但这半年来","from":327.618,"location":2,"to":329.412},{"content":"我们已经夺回到这个地方了哦","from":329.412,"location":2,"to":331.539},{"content":"在推回战线时","from":336.919,"location":2,"to":338.921},{"content":"我们发现这架搁置的共和国机体","from":338.921,"location":2,"to":342.091},{"content":"并跟刻了名字的金属片放在一起","from":342.508,"location":2,"to":345.47},{"content":"联邦一定会将战死者的名字","from":346.054,"location":2,"to":348.514},{"content":"刻在国立公墓的慰灵碑上","from":348.514,"location":2,"to":351.642},{"content":"但我们认为刻在金属片上的","from":351.893,"location":2,"to":354.604},{"content":"你们这575位伙伴的名字","from":354.604,"location":2,"to":356.481},{"content":"应该要留在这里","from":356.481,"location":2,"to":358.733},{"content":"所以就放在这里了","from":358.733,"location":2,"to":360.193},{"content":"我们在记录下金属片的资讯之后","from":361.402,"location":2,"to":363.446},{"content":"就将东西归回原处了, 放心吧","from":363.446,"location":2,"to":366.032},{"content":"如何呀","from":366.991,"location":2,"to":367.992},{"content":"谢谢你们的这番心意","from":369.16,"location":2,"to":371.579},{"content":"但是","from":374.374,"location":2,"to":375.166},{"content":"从特军校毕业之后","from":375.625,"location":2,"to":377.502},{"content":"你们就会正式成为齐亚德联邦的军人","from":377.502,"location":2,"to":381.672},{"content":"而且不久后就会投入实战之中","from":382.632,"location":2,"to":385.843},{"content":"你们将会隶属于我底下的实战部队","from":391.974,"location":2,"to":395.52},{"content":"\"极光\"战队","from":395.52,"location":2,"to":397.605},{"content":"我是一○二八号实验部队的部队长","from":399.482,"location":2,"to":402.026},{"content":"葛蕾蒂．维契尔中校","from":402.026,"location":2,"to":403.569},{"content":"再次请你们多多指教了","from":404.112,"location":2,"to":405.53},{"content":"请多指教","from":406.155,"location":2,"to":407.573},{"content":"不用这样突然把我甩开吧","from":409.075,"location":2,"to":413.162},{"content":"芙蕾德利嘉?","from":413.162,"location":2,"to":414.497},{"content":"那到底是什么啊","from":415.081,"location":2,"to":416.499},{"content":"不准看","from":416.791,"location":2,"to":417.875},{"content":"这可是惊喜","from":417.875,"location":2,"to":419.836},{"content":"惊喜?","from":419.836,"location":2,"to":420.92},{"content":"没错","from":420.92,"location":2,"to":421.629},{"content":"这家伙是怎样啊","from":425.55,"location":2,"to":427.051},{"content":"清道夫?","from":427.051,"location":2,"to":428.136},{"content":"那可是共和国的哦","from":428.136,"location":2,"to":429.345},{"content":"为什么?","from":429.345,"location":2,"to":430.054},{"content":"菲多?","from":430.054,"location":2,"to":430.888},{"content":"你说什么, 辛?","from":431.681,"location":2,"to":433.182},{"content":"你是会将每只宠物 都取一样名字的那种人吗","from":433.205,"location":2,"to":436.76},{"content":"不, 这家伙正是菲多","from":436.936,"location":2,"to":439.063},{"content":"曾与汝等同行的那家伙","from":439.689,"location":2,"to":441.774},{"content":"根据发现这架机体时所做的调查","from":443.317,"location":2,"to":445.778},{"content":"得知其核心组件并没有遭到破坏","from":445.778,"location":2,"to":449.198},{"content":"所以葛蕾蒂他们就进行复原了","from":449.407,"location":2,"to":451.409},{"content":"虽然机体有所更换","from":451.826,"location":2,"to":453.494},{"content":"但确实是如假包换的菲多哦","from":453.494,"location":2,"to":456.289},{"content":"就算外观看上去一样","from":456.289,"location":2,"to":457.874},{"content":"我们还是将性能提升了好几阶哦","from":457.874,"location":2,"to":460.042},{"content":"真的假的…","from":460.543,"location":2,"to":461.544},{"content":"那家伙本来也以为自己已经死了","from":461.794,"location":2,"to":464.839},{"content":"一开始怎样都无法启动","from":464.839,"location":2,"to":466.799},{"content":"但它之所以会醒来","from":467.467,"location":2,"to":469.01},{"content":"就是听见了辛耶的名字","from":469.76,"location":2,"to":472.138},{"content":"你就是我们抵达这里的证明","from":474.307,"location":2,"to":477.977},{"content":"直到化为尘埃为止 这个任务就交给你了","from":478.93,"location":2,"to":481.6},{"content":"你还活着吗","from":485.026,"location":2,"to":487.32},{"content":"我不是要你驻守到化为尘埃吗","from":490.239,"location":2